title: Realfoods Organic Cafe
description: Organic, fair trade cafe operating in the RMIT University City Campus cafeteria. Offerings include raw vegan, gluten-free, sugar-free, and low-fat meals from soups and salads, to mains, desserts, snacks and drinks. A RMIT University Student Union volunteer-run enterprise. Closed during Summer break, re-opens late Feb.
streetAddress: RMIT University, 360 Swanston St, Bldg 8, Lv. 4
